      "comment": "CHOPPER SURE CAN (7) scored off the inside draw two back then finished sixth last start off a wider box (20.90) at this track over 350m. Returns to the scene of his maiden win. Key player on best and worth another chance. TINY DISCO (3) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Casino over 411m behind On Your Broom (24.45) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. The form out of her last race has been franked. Expected to feature in the finish. RIVERSIDE LEVI (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (17.52) in a Grade 5 at Casino. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from four starts. Has ability and can measure up. ULTIMATE FLOYD (2) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
